## How it maps to your AS400 flow

```text
AS400 CREATE
    -> Partner Repository saves user
    -> POST Ping SCIM resource

AS400 UPDATE
    -> Partner Repository updates user
    -> PATCH Ping SCIM resource

AS400 DELETE
    -> Partner Repository disables/deletes user
    -> DELETE or PATCH status in Ping
```

Before using `DELETE`, confirm whether Ping expects physical deletion or only:

```json
{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
```

Identity systems often prefer disabling users instead of deleting them.

