## Recommended service flow

```java
@Transactional
public SnapshotResponse processSnapshot(UserSnapshotRequest request) {
    UserEntity user = userService.createOrUpdate(request);

    try {
        switch (request.getOperation()) {
            case CREATE -> {
                String pingId = pingUserClient.createUser(user);
                user.setPingResourceId(pingId);
            }
            case UPDATE -> pingUserClient.updateUser(
                    user.getPingResourceId(),
                    user
            );
            case DELETE -> pingUserClient.disableUser(
                    user.getPingResourceId()
            );
        }

        user.setPingSyncStatus(PingSyncStatus.SUCCESS);
        user.setPingLastSyncedAt(Instant.now());

    } catch (RuntimeException ex) {
        user.setPingSyncStatus(PingSyncStatus.FAILED);
        user.setPingLastError(ex.getMessage());

        throw new PingIntegrationException(
                "Failed to synchronize user with Ping",
                ex
        );
    }

    return buildResponse(user);
}
```

